title: Amazing Fried Pizza | Antonio Carluccio
description:
RIP dear Antonio. You will be truly missed.  X

You loved him so he's back, the legend that is Antonio Carluccio makes an awesome Pizza that's not baked but fried! It sounds weird, but trust us, it tastes amazing. 

What's your favourite topping for a pizza Food Tubers? Please get in touch in the comments box below.

Would you like to see more of Antonio on the channel? If you shout loud enough we'll ask him very nicely to do some more videos!

In the meantime you can read more of his fantastic recipes in his new book: http://goo.gl/509kJ3

And you can read more great recipes in the Two Greedy Italians book written with Food Tube's very own Gennaro Contaldo: http://goo.gl/yLNlkJ
